Sudowoodo (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0184: Azumarill
Pokémon
#0186: Politoed →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Sudowoodo (TCG Pocket).

Sudowoodo has been featured on 16 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Genesis expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Sudowoodo cards are normally Fighting-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Sudowoodo

Sudowoodo
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
